*----------------------------------------------------------------------*
***INCLUDE MZALTERA_EMAIL_I01.
*----------------------------------------------------------------------*
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*&      Module  USER_COMMAND_9100  INPUT
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*       text
*----------------------------------------------------------------------*
MODULE user_command_9100 INPUT.

  CASE okcode.

    WHEN `PESQUISAR`.
      PERFORM busca_cliente.

    WHEN `GRAVAR`.
      PERFORM atualiza_email.

  ENDCASE.

ENDMODULE.

*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*&      Module  SAIDA_DA_TELA  INPUT
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*       text
*----------------------------------------------------------------------*
MODULE saida_da_tela INPUT.

  IF okcode = 'VOLTAR'.
    LEAVE PROGRAM.
  ENDIF.

ENDMODULE.
